Just some quick motivation

Slide 1: first time I ever met @getbenny before either of us knew I’d eventually sign to @blacksopranofamilyrecords 

Slide 2: fast forward, and he put me in position to get a record deal with @empire 

Slide 3: continue to be a student and soak up all the game

Slide 4: my first CD I ever made.. rightfully titled “Just The Beginning”

Slide 5: I debuted my album with Empire and reached over 1 million streams!

Slide 6 and 7: my “studio” set up was in a small cubby hole in my bedroom. Started with that and eventually opened up my own studio where I eventually met @bsf_cityboy and been on a bigger mission ever since!

HAPPY FIRST BIRTHDAY TO THIS OUTSTANDING PIECE OF ART CALLED “BLEU”

Super proud of my accomplishments thus far, but y’all ain’t seen nothing yet! Over 1 million streams was my personal goal for this album and we SMASHED THAT by a mile! That set the bar for what’s next so get your 🍿🥤 ready.. we just getting warmed up!!

2 record deals, millions of streams, a couple of tours and sold out shows. It still feels like I’m barely breaking the surface in this industry. To some people, it looks like I’ve made it already. But when you get to this level, it becomes clear how far you can really reach. And you want more. You just gotta keep pushing. I’ve got too many reasons to keep putting my foot on they neck, and I can’t think of a single reason to stop. We came a long way but got way more winning to do. Album mode.
